components

Interface IComponent

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Camera, DirectionalLight, Light, PointLight, SpotLight
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CameraComponent, DirectionalLightComponent, FreeCameraComponent, PointLightComponent, SpotLightComponent

    public interface IComponent
    Makes possible that Component's interface can act as Components.
